<% layout("./layouts/boilerplate.ejs") -%>

<div class="container mt-4">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      <div class="form-card">
        <h1 class="fw-bold mb-4">🔒 Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
          At <strong>WanderLust</strong>, your privacy is our top priority. We handle your personal data with the utmost care and transparency.
        </p>
        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-2">📬 What We Collect</h5>
        <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 2;">
          <li>Your name and email (when you sign up or make a booking)</li>
          <li>Location info (only when you choose to share it)</li>
          <li>Listings, reviews, and preferences (to personalize your experience)</li>
        </ul>
        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-2">🤐 What We Don't Do</h5>
        <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 2;">
          <li>We don't sell your data to third parties</li>
          <li>We don't track your browsing without consent</li>
          <li>We don't store passwords in plain text — they're securely hashed</li>
        </ul>
        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-2">🛡️ Security</h5>
        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
          We use industry-standard encryption and secure storage. All payment data is processed through Razorpay's PCI-compliant infrastructure — we never see your card details.
        </p>
        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4 mb-2">🤝 Your Control</h5>
        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8;">
          You're always in charge. Want to delete your data? Contact us and we'll take care of it.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4" style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem;">Last updated: April 2026</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>